  "businessLogic": [
    "Check the featureType from slotsDTO to determine the processing branch.",
    "If featureType is 'CreateNotice': retrieve NoticeInstructionDTO from slotsDTO, transform it to NoticeInstructionEntity via inope transformation 'noticeinstruction-dto-to-entity', set orgCode from request context, and set the entity back onto slotsDTO.",
    "If featureType is 'FundTransfer', 'MultiCreditTransaction', or 'MultiDebitTransaction': retrieve feeApplicableAccounts from slotsDTO; if present, inject them into the currentCommandPayload JSON map and set the updated payload back onto slotsDTO.",
    "For 'FundTransfer' and 'MultiCreditTransaction' (not 'MultiDebitTransaction'): invoke handleFundTransferInitialDeposit to process CREDIT legs \u2014 for each CREDIT leg with initialDeposit='Y', fetch the DepositAccountEntity by account number, set initialDeposit='Y', and set the updated list onto slotsDTO as DEPOSIT_ACCOUNTS_LIST.",
    "For all other featureTypes: retrieve AccountDTO from slotsDTO and map its fields (accountName, accountNumber, cifId, purposeId, purpose, currency) onto a new DepositAccountEntity; set orgCode and initialDeposit='N'.",
    "If DocumentDetailsDTO is present, map its fields (documentCode, documentExpiryDate, documentReceivedDate) onto a new DocumentDetailsEntity and set it onto slotsDTO.",
    "Set the populated DepositAccountEntity onto slotsDTO."
  ],
